  }, "-0.011316*", mdx("br", null), "(0.133721)")))), mdx("br", null), mdx("p", null, "If our hypothesis were to hold, murder should have a more dramatic effect on crime rates during the short term (a two day time frame) compared to a long term (a 30 day time frame). However, both time frames yield similar results -.3686", mdx("em", {
